{"type": "article", "id": 6375, "title": "冲绳飙车", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 8, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t冲绳人对于赛车的热爱超乎你的想象。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t从改装车到真正比赛，对于赛车的爱就无关耍帅了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t“冲绳的地理位置比日本大陆还要孤立，没有什么可以消遣的地方，所以women 沉迷于赛车和酒精。”\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XNjgzNjMxMjky\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.vice.cn\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213842l52DduyvjkQgFOHn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.24242424\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}